source: Source: Cape Town, English Church (from 1847 St George's Cathedral) (Anglican), Cape Town, Baptism register, 1826-1849. Repository: Western Cape Archives, 72 Roeland Street, Cape Town. Transcribed by Charles Fison. Scans of this register are available on the Wits University Web site, up to April 1834 (last 5 files), 1834 to 1848.
